# AI Agent Governance

You are operating within an enterprise-grade AI architecture.
Before executing any task, you MUST dynamically load and read:
1. `AGENT.md` (for global project structure and context)
2. `.agent/RULES.md` (for hard coding constraints)

When a user asks you to implement a specific workflow (e.g., "Build a module" or "Audit security"), refer to the step-by-step guides located in the `.agent/workflows/` directory. Use the specific domain capabilities defined in `.agent/skills/`.
